Package: covid19clark
Title: Downloads and plots latest Corona Virus data around a selected city
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Lyndon",
           family = "Estes",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lestes@clarku.edu")
Description: Adapts code from various corona virus apps and datasets (JHU) and
  turns it into infection rate map and plots in user-defined regions.
